				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-24a1d90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading">
					<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Building food security starts with education</h1>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e8d66c0 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor">
									<p>Our goals start with confronting the issue of finding clear and uncomplicated permaculture education. The chaos of scattered resources, conflicting advice, and no clear starting point often turn eager learners away. Mycelium exists to bridge these gaps. Similar to mycelial systems which connect ecosystems underground, the platform links scattered knowledge together to lower the barrier of learning. Mycelium strengthens permaculture education at its roots, encouraging informed action to support the overarching goal of addressing food insecurity.</p>								</div>
