					<h1 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Why did I build Mycelium at 16?</h1>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-38d9985 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor">
									<p>I built Mycelium at 16 because I wanted uncomplicated permaculture guidance. I got exhausted finding conflicting advice and resources that didn’t apply to me. So I spent the next year building a platform I couldn’t find. With the guidance I got from the Philippine Permaculture Association and hours of curating content, Mycelium is now what I wish existed when I was searching alone at 2 am with too many tabs to count.</p>								</div>
